\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:macro_agg_prod"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

).
 This linkage is established by specifying the type of heterogeneity in firm-level aggregate AI quality levels across firms,
