\begin_inset Formula $\phi(\bar{\alpha})$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Assuming that 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho<0$
\end_inset

 (which implies elasticity of substitution 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma<1$
\end_inset

),
 indicating that industry-level production exhibits some degree of complementarity,
